description: Quattrocento Sans is a classic, elegant and sober typeface family. Warm, readable and not intrusive. It's the perfect sans-serif companion for Quattrocento. The wide and open letterforms and large x-height make it very legible for body text at small sizes. All the tiny details that only shows up at bigger sizes make it also great for display use. Join the project at www.impallari.com/projects
